]][[Category:kk]][[Category:::Makimuku Katsuyama Kofun]][[Category:kk]][[Category::kk]][[Category:kk]][[Category:::kk]][[Category:kk]][[Category::kk]][[Category:kk]][[Category:::dd]][[Category:kk]][[Category::kk]][[Category:kk]][[Category:::kk]][[Category:kk]][[Category::kk]][[Category:kk]][[Category:::properly attributed pages]] [[Category:kkkk]] [[Category:kkkkk]] [[ja:纒向勝山古墳]] {{⚠️🚨COPIED from EverybodyWiki ❗❕⚠️😡😤Please respect Licence CC-BY-SA ❗}} {{Source Wikipedia}}

